🎵 Music Application (Mobile App UI)
This repository contains the UI/UX design for a Music Application designed using Figma. The application focuses on providing an intuitive and seamless user experience with features like personalized recommendations, smart search, and high-quality audio streaming.

🔗 Figma Design Link
Click here to view the design

✨ Features
🎨 Intuitive Interface: Clean, minimalistic design with clearly labeled buttons and easy navigation.
🎵 Personalized Recommendations: AI-driven suggestions based on listening history.
🔍 Smart Search: Advanced search with predictive text and voice search options.
📂 Customizable Playlists: Create, edit, and share playlists with drag-and-drop functionality.
🔊 High-Quality Audio: Supports high-fidelity audio streaming.
